          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Poison (Ex):</strong></span> Injury, Fortitude DC 13, initial damage sleep for 1 minute, secondary damage sleep for another 5d6 minutes. The save DC is Constitution-based and includes a +2 racial bonus.</p>
