      <div class="sect2" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="title"><a name="id1962792"/>Construction</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersH-I106"/>
        <p>A <a href="ch67s10.html#MonstersH-I103">homunculus</a> is shaped from a mixture of clay, ashes, mandrake root, spring water, and one pint of the creator's own blood. The materials cost 50 gp. The creature's master may assemble the body or hire someone else to do the job. Creating the body requires a DC 12 <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills91">Craft</a> (sculpting) check or a DC 12 <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills91">Craft</a> (pottery) check.</p>
        <p>After the body is sculpted, it is animated through an extended magical ritual that requires a specially prepared laboratory or workroom, similar to an alchemist's laboratory and costing 500 gp to establish. If the creator is personally constructing the creature's body, the building and ritual can be performed together.</p>
        <p>A <a href="ch67s10.html#MonstersH-I103">homunculus</a> with more than 2 Hit Dice can be created, but each additional Hit Die adds +2,000 gp to the cost to create.</p>
        <p><a href="ch20.html#MonsterFeats9">Craft Construct</a>, <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch43.html#SpellsA-B23">arcane eye</a></em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch48.html#SpellsM-O40">mirror image</a></em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch48.html#SpellsM-O31">mending</a></em></span>, <span class="emphasis"><em/></span> caster must be at least 4th level; Price - (never sold); Cost 1,050 gp + 78 XP.</p>
